I won't let you off.

143
00:08:37,909 --> 00:08:38,870
You hear me?

144
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:42,720
Mrs. Shi.

145
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:44,860
Today I'm going

146
00:08:44,860 --> 00:08:46,260
to tell you very clearly.

147
00:08:47,150 --> 00:08:48,600
Whatever happened to Shi Yue

148
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:50,400
had nothing to do with me before,

149
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:52,280
