166
00:09:24,550 --> 00:09:27,030
My relationship with him
has indeed been bad.

167
00:09:27,030 --> 00:09:28,440
But do you know why?

168
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:30,720
Because I lost interest

169
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:31,910
in him long ago.

170
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:34,530
I actually hoped Hao Meili

171
