No.

188
00:10:13,710 --> 00:10:14,870
-Officer Zhou.
-Zhou Mi.

189
00:10:14,870 --> 00:10:15,550
Alright.

190
00:10:15,630 --> 00:10:17,160
Zhou Mi, please hear us out.

191
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:17,790
Officer Zhou.

192
00:10:17,790 --> 00:10:19,150
-Zhou Mi.
-Officer Zhou.

193
00:10:19,150 --> 00:10:19,910
That's enough.

194
00:10:19,910 --> 00:10:20,710
Officer Zhou!

195
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:22,330
We've been waiting for you all day!

196
00:10:21,060 --> 00:10:23,270
[Police]

197
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:22,840
Officer Zhou!

198
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:23,510
Enough!

199
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:24,840
Mentor.

200
00:10:25,870 --> 00:10:27,750
