210
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:42,120
The elderly couple
at the entrance just now,

211
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:42,890
why wouldn't you even

212
00:10:42,890 --> 00:10:43,750
let them speak?

213
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,770
They might have legitimate concerns.

214
00:10:45,770 --> 00:10:47,550
They could be relatives of someone
involved in the case.

215
00:10:47,550 --> 00:10:49,810
Or they might want to provide some leads.

216
00:10:50,870 --> 00:10:52,510
If you're unhappy with my way
of handling cases,

217
00:10:52,510 --> 00:10:54,320
go find Captain Gao first thing
tomorrow morning

218
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:55,450
and get a new mentor.

219
00:10:56,270 --> 00:10:57,000
Also,

220
00:10:57,630 --> 00:10:59,480
