235
00:11:59,270 --> 00:12:00,170
so logically he should have been able

236
00:12:00,170 --> 00:12:01,970
to easily restore these things.

237
00:12:04,910 --> 00:12:05,870
But,

238
00:12:06,440 --> 00:12:07,670
he only took

239
00:12:07,670 --> 00:12:08,960
Shi Yue's phone,

240
00:12:09,550 --> 00:12:11,080
