243
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:15,840
and illogical aspects everywhere.

244
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:19,290
We previously deduced

245
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:21,360
that Su Muxin and Qu Tong
were conspiring together,

246
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:22,670
that Qu Tong was helping Su Muxin,

247
00:12:22,670 --> 00:12:24,670
and that Su Muxin was hiding in Yunzhou.

248
00:12:24,670 --> 00:12:25,960
But now I think

249
00:12:26,750 --> 00:12:28,440
our deduction was wrong.

250
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:31,840
Maybe all of Qu Tong's suspicious behavior

251
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:33,570
had nothing to do with Su Muxin.

252
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:34,550
Why do you say

253
00:12:34,550 --> 00:12:36,550
your previous deduction was wrong?

254
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:40,580
Qu Tong is someone

255
00:12:40,790 --> 00:12:42,120
who's extremely cautious

256
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:43,580
and doesn't trust anyone.

257
00:12:43,670 --> 00:12:45,150
