259
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:48,000
But today

260
00:12:48,960 --> 00:12:50,750
when she was facing Shi Yue's mother...

261
00:12:50,750 --> 00:12:51,720
Say something!

262
00:12:51,750 --> 00:12:52,870
Yes, you're right.

263
00:12:53,670 --> 00:12:55,870
There was the mix of old and new grudges.

264
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:58,680
Her reaction was emotional.

265
00:12:59,080 --> 00:12:59,670
Because I lost interest

266
00:12:59,670 --> 00:13:00,750
in him long ago.

267
00:13:03,270 --> 00:13:04,870
I think that was the real her.

268
00:13:05,790 --> 00:13:07,520
Her relationship with Su Muxin

269
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:08,600
is probably

270
00:13:09,550 --> 00:13:11,550
different from what she's showing.

271
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:12,910
Without some

272
00:13:12,910 --> 00:13:13,870
special reason,

273
00:13:14,550 --> 00:13:16,080
