00:15:59,630 --> 00:16:00,490
Officer Zhou.

290
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:02,060
I'm Ms. Zhang.

291
00:16:02,290 --> 00:16:04,650
[Teaching Building]

292
00:16:04,270 --> 00:16:05,360
When school starts again,

293
00:16:05,360 --> 00:16:06,200
we'll all be moving

294
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:07,330
to the new district.

295
00:16:07,750 --> 00:16:09,480
This place will be demolished.

296
00:16:09,910 --> 00:16:10,790
To be honest,

297
00:16:11,030 --> 00:16:12,690
I'm quite reluctant to leave.

298
00:16:13,320 --> 00:16:14,360
This school was built

299
00:16:14,360 --> 00:16:15,870
back in the 1970s.

300
00:16:16,790 --> 00:16:18,000
You called

301
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:20,270
to ask about Qu Tong,

302
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:21,150
Su Muxin,

303
00:16:21,240 --> 00:16:22,790
and Hao Meili from the 1986 cohort.

304
00:16:22,790 --> 00:16:24,030
I've done my best

305
00:16:24,120 --> 00:16:24,720
to collect all the things

306
00:16:24,720 --> 00:16:25,840
they left behind

307
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:26,960
back then.

308
00:16:27,360 --> 00:16:28,960
But it has been a long time.

309
00:16:29,270 --> 00:16:30,530
There's not much left.

310
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:31,080
Okay.

311
00:16:39,790 --> 00:16:41,200
Here's everything I have on them.

312
00:16:41,200 --> 00:16:41,670
Okay.

313
00:16:45,600 --> 00:16:46,200
[Hao Meili, Class 1, Senior 3]

314
00:16:46,250 --> 00:16:48,580
[Li Li, Class 2, Senior 3]

315
00:16:48,710 --> 00:16:49,830
[Su Muxin, Class 1, Senior 3]

316
00:16:51,600 --> 00:16:53,480
Do you have a strong impression
of Su Muxin?

317
00:16:53,480 --> 00:16:55,480
Su Muxin was the class monitor then,

318
00:16:55,480 --> 00:16:56,810
with excellent grades.

319
00:16:57,210 --> 00:16:58,740
[Qu Tong, Class 1, Senior 3]

320
00:16:57,630 --> 00:16:59,030
He was from Chen Village,

321
00:16:59,600 --> 00:17:01,080
far from the county town.

322
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:02,960
I remember he only had his mother,

323
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:03,720
no father.

324
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:04,560
Thank you.

325
00:17:05,880 --> 00:17:07,740
There were no highways back then.

326
00:17:07,920 --> 00:17:09,000
Going home

327
00:17:09,109 --> 00:17:10,880
would take him an entire night.

328
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:12,349
So at that time,

329
00:17:12,720 --> 00:17:14,180
he lived in the dormitory.

330
00:17:14,349 --> 00:17:15,270
In the 1980s,

331
00:17:15,400 --> 00:17:17,200
getting into college was very difficult.

332
00:17:17,200 --> 00:17:19,260
So the whole village was proud of him.

333
00:17:32,720 --> 00:17:34,920
Ms. Zhang, I'm innocent.

334
00:17:35,400 --> 00:17:36,640
In today's class meeting,

335
00:17:36,640 --> 00:17:38,350
although I apologized,

336
00:17:38,720 --> 00:17:40,000
it wasn't sincere.

337
00:17:40,350 --> 00:17:42,030
I really didn't do that.

338
00:17:43,550 --> 00:17:44,400
It has been

339
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:46,030
over ten years.

340
00:17:47,590 --> 00:17:49,190
But I still can't get over it.

341
00:17:50,640 --> 00:17:52,200
I didn't handle it well back then.

342
00:17:52,200 --> 00:17:53,750
I want Qu Tong to apologize!

343
00:17:53,170 --> 00:17:56,760
[1986]

344
00:17:58,960 --> 00:17:59,640
Hao Meili.

345
00:18:00,270 --> 00:18:01,680
I want her to apologize.

346
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:14,880
I'm sorry.

347
00:18:38,830 --> 00:18:40,490
What kind of person
is Qu Tong?

348
00:18:40,550 --> 00:18:42,270
In my impression, she was
very introverted,

349
00:18:42,270 --> 00:18:43,000
quiet,

350
00:18:43,960 --> 00:18:45,400
and strictly supervised by her family.

351
00:18:45,400 --> 00:18:46,790
So she never attended

352
00:18:46,830 --> 00:18:48,240
any gatherings with classmates.

353
00:18:48,240 --> 00:18:49,570
She didn't talk much,

354
00:18:49,880 --> 00:18:51,540
and basically had no friends.

355
00:18:52,200 --> 00:18:53,110
Vixen.

356
00:18:53,310 --> 00:18:54,970
The vixen of No. 1 High School.

357
00:18:57,550 --> 00:18:58,550
But she was very smart,

358
00:18:58,550 --> 00:18:59,880
with excellent grades.

359
00:19:00,200 --> 00:19:02,000
Before Hao Meili transferred
to our school,

360
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:03,860
she always ranked first in exams.

361
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:05,830
After that incident happened,

362
00:19:05,960 --> 00:19:08,020
it had a huge emotional impact on her,

363
00:19:08,880 --> 00:19:11,280
even affecting her academic performance.

364
00:19:11,510 --> 00:19:13,040
But she recovered quickly,

365
00:19:13,270 --> 00:19:14,240
and eventually

366
00:19:14,270 --> 00:19:15,590
got into college successfully.

367
00:19:15,590 --> 00:19:16,830
So I think

368
00:19:18,070 --> 00:19:20,330
she might appear fragile on the outside,

369
00:19:20,400 --> 00:19:21,400
but actually

370
00:19:22,160 --> 00:19:23,820
she was a very resilient girl.

371
00:19:26,550 --> 00:19:27,270
Well,

372
00:19:27,880 --> 00:19:29,880
was Qu Tong responsible for

373
00:19:30,680 --> 00:19:32,140
the bullying of Hao Meili?

374
00:19:33,160 --> 00:19:33,740
There's no way

375
00:19:33,740 --> 00:19:35,470
to verify this matter anymore.

376
00:19:36,160 --> 00:19:37,790
But I don't think it was her.

377
00:19:38,350 --> 00:19:39,610
Was Su Muxin involved?

378
00:19:40,630 --> 00:19:41,830
I'm not sure about that.

379
00:19:41,830 --> 00:19:42,590
Qu Tong seems

380
00:19:42,610 --> 00:19:43,690
a bit pitiful.

381
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:44,680
Indeed.

382
00:19:45,600 --> 00:19:46,900
You feel sorry for her?

383
00:19:47,440 --> 00:19:48,880
Do you know what she is?

384
00:19:48,920 --> 00:19:49,680
What?

385
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:52,830
The vixen of No. 1 High School.

386
00:19:53,880 --> 00:19:54,790
Vixen.

387
00:19:54,830 --> 00:19:56,150
Vixen.

388
00:19:56,350 --> 00:19:57,130
You feel sorry for her?

389
00:19:57,130 --> 00:19:58,190
That vixen.

390
00:19:59,350 --> 00:20:00,070
Feel sorry?

391
00:20:00,090 --> 00:20:01,480
Why feel sorry for her?

392
00:20:01,960 --> 00:20:03,110
She's just a vixen.

393
00:20:08,880 --> 00:20:15,230
[Sanjie Restaurant]

394
00:20:13,590 --> 00:20:15,120
Maybe we missed something.

395
00:20:15,960 --> 00:20:16,640
Otherwise we shouldn't

396
00:20:16,640 --> 00:20:18,300
have failed to catch Su Muxin.

397
00:20:20,380 --> 00:20:21,200
So you called me here

398
00:20:21,200 --> 00:20:23,130
to see if there are any other leads?

399
00:20:23,250 --> 00:20:26,000
[Sanjie Restaurant]

400
00:20:29,990 --> 00:20:33,230
[Open]

401
00:20:33,880 --> 00:20:35,080
Mr. Zhang, look here.

402
00:20:35,830 --> 00:20:36,590
From here you can see

403
00:20:36,590 --> 00:20:38,050
our car across the street.

404
00:20:39,200 --> 00:20:40,310
Qu Tong must have spotted

405
00:20:40,310 --> 00:20:41,720
that we were following her

406
00:20:41,720 --> 00:20:43,200
and passed the message to Su Muxin.

407
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:44,330
It must be like that.

408
00:20:44,550 --> 00:20:45,790
Our car was parked right over there.

409
00:20:45,650 --> 00:20:48,220
[Sanjie Restaurant]

410
00:20:48,680 --> 00:20:50,000
Besides Qu Tong,

411
00:20:50,030 --> 00:20:51,880
was Su Muxin close

412
00:20:52,110 --> 00:20:53,640
with any other classmates?

413
00:20:54,590 --> 00:20:56,070
I heard from students

414
00:20:56,090 --> 00:20:57,080
in his year

415
00:20:57,200 --> 00:20:58,770
that after Su Muxin got into college,

416
00:20:58,770 --> 00:21:00,640
he cut off contact
with his former classmates.

417
00:21:00,640 --> 00:21:01,640
Later, someone

418
00:21:01,750 --> 00:21:03,110
ran into him in Yunzhou.

419
00:21:03,680 --> 00:21:06,400
It was said he worked
at the Industry and Commerce Bureau

420
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:08,260
and had become a senior official.

421
00:21:12,410 --> 00:21:13,270
At that time, Qu Tong's car

422
00:21:13,270 --> 00:21:14,350
was parked right here.

423
00:21:14,350 --> 00:21:15,410
After she went out,

424
00:21:15,720 --> 00:21:17,450
she got something from her car.

425
00:21:17,790 --> 00:21:18,510
We didn't notice

426
00:21:18,510 --> 00:21:19,770
anything suspicious.

427
00:21:20,110 --> 00:21:20,830
After getting off the car,

428
00:21:20,830 --> 00:21:22,030
she walked along this road

429
00:21:22,030 --> 00:21:22,960
straight ahead,

430
00:21:23,550 --> 00:21:24,950
never leaving our sight.

431
00:21:26,400 --> 00:21:28,330
Where exactly did things go wrong?

432
00:21:34,110 --> 00:21:34,830
Details.

433
00:21:36,030 --> 00:21:37,000
There must be some details

434
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:38,060
that we've missed.

435
00:21:43,720 --> 00:21:44,270
Hello.

436
00:21:44,010 --> 00:21:45,930
[Yunzhou Trading Company]

437
00:21:45,240 --> 00:21:45,970
I'm here to see Mr. Li.

438
00:21:45,970 --> 00:21:49,700
[Yunzhou Trading Company]

439
00:21:47,350 --> 00:21:49,480
Mr. Li, Officer Zhou is here to see you.

440
00:21:50,270 --> 00:21:51,000
Please come in.

441
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:52,200
Officer Zhou from Dongjiang, right?

442
00:21:52,200 --> 00:21:52,790
Hello, Mr. Li.

443
00:21:52,790 --> 00:21:54,250
Hello, please have a seat.

444
00:21:55,310 --> 00:21:56,680
I'm here today to ask you

445
00:21:56,720 --> 00:21:58,310
about someone.

446
00:21:58,400 --> 00:21:59,060
About whom?

447
00:21:59,110 --> 00:21:59,880
Su Muxin.

448
00:22:00,720 --> 00:22:02,320
Mr. Su from Zhuo'er Jewelry?

449
00:22:03,310 --> 00:22:04,280
In 1994,

450
00:22:04,310 --> 00:22:05,240
Su Muxin was transferred back

451
00:22:05,240 --> 00:22:07,480
to serve as deputy section chief
at Yunzhou Industry and Commerce Bureau.

452
00:22:07,480 --> 00:22:08,070
At that time,

453
00:22:08,070 --> 00:22:09,270
you hadn't resigned
to go into business yet.

454
00:22:09,270 --> 00:22:10,510
You were his superior,

455
00:22:10,510 --> 00:22:11,240
weren't you?

456
00:22:11,550 --> 00:22:12,070
Yes.

457
00:22:12,930 --> 00:22:13,720
But after he married Qu Tong,

458
00:22:13,720 --> 00:22:14,480
he resigned

459
00:22:14,510 --> 00:22:16,350
not long after.

460
00:22:16,640 --> 00:22:18,440
Later I also went into business.

461
00:22:18,960 --> 00:22:20,360
We didn't interact much.

462
00:22:21,590 --> 00:22:22,720
You know Qu Tong too?

463
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:25,370
Just a coincidence.

464
00:22:25,830 --> 00:22:26,880
They reunited

465
00:22:26,920 --> 00:22:27,920
at the Industry and Commerce Bureau.

466
00:22:27,920 --> 00:22:29,180
I was there at the time.

467
00:22:30,400 --> 00:22:30,920
Director Li.

468
00:22:30,660 --> 00:22:34,250
[1994]

469
00:22:31,030 --> 00:22:31,490
Come in.

470
00:22:35,160 --> 00:22:36,240
Could you please check

471
00:22:36,240 --> 00:22:36,920
if their paperwork

472
00:22:36,920 --> 00:22:38,120
is missing anything?

473
00:22:38,480 --> 00:22:39,550
This is similar to the case

474
00:22:39,550 --> 00:22:40,350
you handled last time.

475
00:22:40,350 --> 00:22:40,680
Sure.

476
00:22:42,270 --> 00:22:42,960
Su Muxin.

477
00:22:56,740 --> 00:22:58,270
I wrote you many letters,

478
00:22:58,780 --> 00:23:00,040
but you never replied.

479
00:23:04,120 --> 00:23:04,920
I even called the school

480
00:23:04,920 --> 00:23:06,000
to confirm

481
00:23:06,760 --> 00:23:08,420
that the address was correct.

482
00:23:10,350 --> 00:23:10,950
Is that so?

483
00:23:14,760 --> 00:23:15,820
It doesn't matter.

484
00:23:17,700 --> 00:23:19,560
The good thing is we've met again.

485
00:23:23,200 --> 00:23:23,890
Tong.

486
00:23:26,200 --> 00:23:27,130
We should go now.

487
00:23:30,310 --> 00:23:31,310
Section Chief Su.

488
00:23:31,910 --> 00:23:33,110
About the paperwork,

489
00:23:33,310 --> 00:23:34,840
I'll leave it in your hands.

490
00:23:34,920 --> 00:23:35,850
You're welcome.

491
00:23:38,730 --> 00:23:42,060
[General Office]

492
00:23:38,840 --> 00:23:39,740
Tong, let's go.

493
00:23:45,330 --> 00:23:46,530
Since you're so busy,

494
00:23:47,810 --> 00:23:49,340
I won't bother you anymore.

495
00:23:57,420 --> 00:23:58,750
This is my pager number.

496
00:23:59,550 --> 00:24:00,550
I'll be going now.

497
00:24:05,130 --> 00:24:06,240
[Announcement Board
of Yunzhou Industry and Commerce Bureau]

498
00:24:13,200 --> 00:24:14,770
This high school classmate of yours

499
00:24:14,770 --> 00:24:16,300
is Qu Lijun's daughter?

500
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:17,730
Their family

501
00:24:19,060 --> 00:24:20,160
is quite well-off.

502
00:24:21,230 --> 00:24:23,060
He made his fortune in Guangdong.

503
00:24:23,060 --> 00:24:25,220
A couple of years ago, he took over
a factory in the county,

504
00:24:25,220 --> 00:24:27,100
specializing in jewelry processing.

505
00:24:27,100 --> 00:24:28,040
It's going quite well.

506
00:24:28,040 --> 00:24:28,620
And

507
00:24:28,650 --> 00:24:30,350
they've even landed a contract

508
00:24:30,350 --> 00:24:32,240
with that high-end brand Jinfeng
from Guangdong.

509
00:24:32,240 --> 00:24:33,350
They're really expanding.

510
00:24:33,350 --> 00:24:33,950
That's why

511
00:24:34,130 --> 00:24:36,260
they're applying for land to scale up.

512
00:24:37,140 --> 00:24:38,470
Take a good look at this.

513
00:24:47,400 --> 00:24:48,400
Section Chief Su.

514
00:25:00,210 --> 00:25:07,480
[Yunzhou Trading Company]

515
00:25:00,290 --> 00:25:01,690
I'm sorry, Officer Zhou.

516
00:25:01,750 --> 00:25:03,210
I couldn't be of much help.

517
00:25:03,640 --> 00:25:04,500
About his case,

518
00:25:04,890 --> 00:25:06,620
my knowledge is quite limited.

519
00:25:08,480 --> 00:25:09,310
What do you

520
00:25:09,790 --> 00:25:11,270
think of Su Muxin?

521
00:25:13,550 --> 00:25:15,270
Speaking of Su Muxin,

522
00:25:17,640 --> 00:25:19,840
I think he's destined for great things.

523
00:25:20,030 --> 00:25:21,630
He's decisive in his actions

524
00:25:21,640 --> 00:25:22,770
and at the same time,

525
00:25:23,160 --> 00:25:25,220
he's hardly influenced by emotions.

526
00:25:25,640 --> 00:25:26,770
He's very rational.

527
00:25:27,490 --> 00:25:28,090
Of course,

528
00:25:28,640 --> 00:25:30,170
from another perspective,

529
00:25:30,510 --> 00:25:32,710
some might find him a bit cold-hearted.

530
00:25:33,950 --> 00:25:34,560
I see.

531
00:25:35,350 --> 00:25:36,310
Thanks for your cooperation.

532
00:25:36,310 --> 00:25:37,040
My pleasure.

533
00:25:37,170 --> 00:25:37,960
Please don't see me out.

534
00:25:37,960 --> 00:25:38,560
Take care.

535
00:25:48,960 --> 00:25:50,590
Where did we go wrong?

536
00:25:51,160 --> 00:25:51,850
Otherwise we shouldn't

537
00:25:51,850 --> 00:25:53,510
have failed to catch Su Muxin.

538
00:25:54,370 --> 00:25:56,230
It's fine. Let's head back first.

539
00:26:13,070 --> 00:26:13,640
Hello.

540
00:26:14,830 --> 00:26:16,290
Okay, I'll be right there.

541
00:26:19,270 --> 00:26:19,640
Mentor,

542
00:26:19,640 --> 00:26:21,500
I think there's one possibility.

543
00:26:21,600 --> 00:26:22,680
Qu Tong and Su Muxin

544
00:26:22,720 --> 00:26:23,440
did actually arrange

545
00:26:23,440 --> 00:26:24,920
to meet at Sanjie Restaurant.

546
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:25,960
But she discovered early on

547
00:26:25,960 --> 00:26:27,490
that we were following her.

548
00:26:27,590 --> 00:26:28,790
You were inside the restaurant then,

549
00:26:28,790 --> 00:26:30,450
while I was watching at the entrance.

550
00:26:30,450 --> 00:26:31,550
When Qu Tong left,

551
00:26:31,590 --> 00:26:33,450
her movements were a bit strange.

552
00:26:34,630 --> 00:26:36,830
But only now do I realize what was wrong.

553
00:26:36,920 --> 00:26:38,000
After she went out,

554
00:26:38,020 --> 00:26:40,020
she went to her car to get something.

555
00:26:42,110 --> 00:26:44,040
There was a clear unlocking sound.

556
00:26:47,510 --> 00:26:48,480
But when

557
00:26:48,510 --> 00:26:50,000
we came back with her,

558
00:26:53,440 --> 00:26:54,240
she made

559
00:26:54,270 --> 00:26:55,730
a fake unlocking gesture,

560
00:26:56,680 --> 00:26:58,080
with no unlocking sound.

561
00:26:59,880 --> 00:27:00,440
Goodbye.

562
00:27:02,310 --> 00:27:04,160
She wasn't getting something earlier.

563
00:27:04,160 --> 00:27:05,890
She was just unlocking the car.

564
00:27:07,680 --> 00:27:09,310
If we follow this reasoning,

565
00:27:10,200 --> 00:27:11,440
when we were following her,

566
00:27:11,440 --> 00:27:12,750
her nervous expression

567
00:27:12,750 --> 00:27:13,950
and looking back at us

568
00:27:14,160 --> 00:27:16,060
wasn't because she feared
us following her,

569
00:27:16,060 --> 00:27:17,790
but she feared we wouldn't follow her.

570
00:27:17,790 --> 00:27:18,350
Right.

571
00:27:19,230 --> 00:27:19,830
I suspect

572
00:27:19,880 --> 00:27:21,140
that during this time,

573
00:27:21,320 --> 00:27:22,680
Su Muxin had already hidden

574
00:27:22,680 --> 00:27:24,280
in the trunk of Qu Tong's car.

575
00:28:06,580 --> 00:28:10,410
[Restroom]

576
00:28:25,070 --> 00:28:25,510
Hello.

577
00:28:25,550 --> 00:28:26,810
Are you here for a meal?

578
00:28:30,920 --> 00:28:31,780
[Restroom,
Caution, Wet Floor]

579
00:28:31,960 --> 00:28:34,870
[Friendly Reminder,
Caution, Wet Floor]

580
00:28:53,680 --> 00:28:54,480
